text: Jessica Zimmerman (born 21 February 1995) is an Australian water polo player. She was part of the Australian team at the 2017 World Aquatics Championships, 2015 Summer Universiade, and 2019 Summer Universiade. == References == == Others websites== * Aussie Stingers - Jessica Zimmerman | Water Polo Australia * News | Water Polo Australia * Water polo: Australian ladies about the 17th FINA World Championships Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Australian water polo players
